{"tid":1675282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［狂賀] 繼慈母推介嘅明日大嶼之後 又有單160億嘅工程即將審議","createTime":"2019-10-25T18:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T18:33:20.000Z","uid":130542,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"955574e676f26535deb47289c6e2ae47a483ddbb","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:09:18.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到陳沛然醫生fb出左篇文 係有關財委會第一項審議項目係一宗涉及160億嘅工程項目<br />\n<a href=\"https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/10/t2.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdoctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F10%2Ft2.html%3Fm%3D1&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=c233fbe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://doctordaddysoccer.blogspot.com/2019/10/t2.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n相信有睇電視都知林鄭份施政報告賣廣告果陣依然死唔斷氣咁提明日大嶼 而佢本人亦三番四次慈母上身咁話為下一代著想 明日大嶼係有必要性 相信大家都知佢嘅死亡之吻有幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且佢都知自己坐唔耐 所以能夠用餘下任期盡全力愛護香港同香港人亦好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但香港國庫能唔能夠負擔咁龐大嘅開支？(101%會超支+延誤)<br />\n<br />\n依家又有一單160億嘅T2主幹路及茶果嶺隧道建造工程<br />\n加上內文有提及現時已有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">4單工程</span></span></strong>嘅超支金額仲係未知數<br />\n而唔好忘記 財委會主席係我地辛苦工作左幾十年嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收成波</span></span></strong> 配合建制出盡奶力投票助攻 議案絕對係話過就過 就算聽日話草擬用晒個庫房你地港豬都無得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以不久嘅將來 我地全香港人除左養一大班新移民同廢老之外 仲有千千萬萬條債等住我地去還<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果話一粒精子令到香港咁樣<br />\n同樣地你地班人連最基本嘅投票都唔投 任由建制鐵飛保送班建制入議會 咁你地有咩資格睇住新聞屌佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地唔投票一樣令到議會比建制玩晒&mdash;&gt;不停撥款搞5千萬噴水池、8萬蚊個單車位、避唔到雨嘅避雨亭&mdash;&gt;所有議案話過就過&mdash;&gt;23條、剔除廣東話、大陸醫生可以落香港執業、智能識別等等<br />\n到時唔好話有冇下一代 香港人依一代生唔生活到落去都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾個月遊行仲有人發起係咁派選民登記表 好記得有班未夠歲數嘅學生叫我地好好運用手中一票幫佢地守護個香港<br />\n你地仲記唔記得呀？香港人 可唔可以有啲記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">仲有就係160億依單野係咪過硬？完全冇辦法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n幾時可以唔使再睇依啲政治消息 還番個正常香港比我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000a3eee5688edb0180474df95e05014271ef274","tid":1675282,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUPo8oT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUPo8oT.gif&h=0b30e983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25ea52e0c3e09972a44fbccd67716611f3a2f014","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"內文有啲長 希望大家比少少耐性睇晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a755fc467fd3a751dd81247fd3b215ad779513f","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"自推10下<br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"a826502a4eaa2f6d15568ea89da681702dd023c7","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fc1ffbccb2ffe90fb8da1437720e43e6113584","tid":1675282,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"806b128abf5808ecfbc191b019af2bd62eeb5b7c","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:03.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d379f664ff75dd2b64b4cc0ce02b307c39dca16d","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"4/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93e179b461c777997e4c78a89ef54f84182b219","tid":1675282,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"收成波一定要入制裁list"},{"pid":"3e46e20e68f247bbc53a53e463048e819b58b149","tid":1675282,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"作為一個 Civil 撚加道路使用者，真心想中九龍幹線過到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8234266b201db29b4ca0b270d99587ae01ebfa3","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f1ecefcaf008bc0e65eeb56fae0994464bd385","tid":1675282,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:14:04.000Z","msg":"又送錢俾支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b6b1a2123549214ed3c09e2e3b4bd34090d02c","tid":1675282,"uid":130542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:14:43.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6261253787fd638d2adf502f7ce8f8675b41260f","tid":1675282,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e46e20e68f247bbc53a53e463048e819b58b149","tid":1675282,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"作為一個 Civil 撚加道路使用者，真心想中九龍幹線過到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:14:47.000Z","msg":"可惜呢個唔係民選政府，本身就算係好事佢都會扭曲成為中共服務<br />\n智能燈柱就係一個例子"},{"pid":"2852b60cde8f7120e922a80fd68d40764ffd7274","tid":1675282,"uid":64702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e46e20e68f247bbc53a53e463048e819b58b149","tid":1675282,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"作為一個 Civil 撚加道路使用者，真心想中九龍幹線過到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif